<node CREATED="1566553719044" ID="ID_262788906" MODIFIED="1566553719044" TEXT="Philosophy 103: Introduction to Logic Translation of Propositions. Abstract: Some well-known techniques for translating ordinary language sentences into standard form categorical propositions are explained." />
</node>
