<node CREATED="1566553719044" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1056849373" LINK="https://open.umn.edu/opentextbooks/textbooks/54" MODIFIED="1566553719044" TEXT="An Introduction to Formal Logic - Open Textbook Library">
<node CREATED="1566553719044" ID="ID_68131186" MODIFIED="1566553719044" TEXT="The simplification comes at a cost and different formal languages are suited to translating different parts of natural language. The book is designed to provide a semesters worth of material for an introductory college course. It would be possible to use the book only for sentential logic by skipping chapters 4-5 and parts of chapter 6." />
