<node CREATED="1566553719058" ID="ID_145828157" MODIFIED="1566553719058" TEXT="Quite simply a context free language is a language that can be generated by a context free grammar. Some languages are context free and some are not. For example it seems plausible that English is a context free language. That is it is probably possible to write a context free grammar that generates all (and only) the sentences that native " />
