<node CREATED="1566553719059" ID="ID_1500435595" MODIFIED="1566553719059" TEXT="This distinguishes abstract syntax trees from concrete syntax trees traditionally designated parse trees which are typically built by a parser during the source code translation and compiling process. Once built additional information is added to the AST by means of subsequent processing e.g. contextual analysis." />
