<node CREATED="1566553719076" ID="ID_1787897128" MODIFIED="1566553719076" TEXT="This is a hierarchy so every language of type 3 is also of types 2 1 and 0; every language of type 2 is also of types 1 and 0 etc. The distinction between languages can be seen by examining the structure of the production rules of their corresponding grammar or the nature of the automata which can be used to identify them." />
</node>
