<node CREATED="1566553719076" ID="ID_1266313496" MODIFIED="1566553719076" TEXT="The Chomsky hierarchy sometimes known as the Chomsky-Sch&#195;&#188;tzenberger hierarchy is a hierarchy of formal grammatical systems for describing various classes of languages; the hierarchy can apply to both human and computer languages. This hierarchy was first published in 1956 by the linguist Chomsky." />
