<node CREATED="1566553719089" ID="ID_97415628" MODIFIED="1566553719089" TEXT="Post Correspondence Problem. In this section we will discuss the undecidability of string and not of Turing machines. The undecidability of the string is determined with the help of Posts Correspondence Problem (PCP). Let us define the PCP. The Posts correspondence problem consists of two lists of string that are of equal length over the input." />
