<node CREATED="1566553719089" ID="ID_375428456" MODIFIED="1566553719089" TEXT="The Post correspondence problem remains undecidable if consists of 9 letters. The decidability status is open if the cardinality of is a fixed number between 3 and 8 (inclusive). The Post correspondence problem is closely linked with equality sets which are important in the representation theory of formal languages." />
