<node CREATED="1566553719089" ID="ID_773437413" MODIFIED="1566553719089" TEXT="POST&#226;&#8364;&#8482;s CORRESPONDENCE PROBLEM 1. POST&#226;&#8364;&#8482;s CORRESPONDENCE PROBLEM 2. &#226;&#8364;&#162; General Objective: &#226;&#8364;&#8220; to understand the concept of PCP &#226;&#8364;&#162; Specific Objectives &#226;&#8364;&#8220; State the objective of PCP &#226;&#8364;&#8220; Define PCP problem &#226;&#8364;&#8220; Check whether the PCP instance have a solution or not." />
