<node CREATED="1566553719090" ID="ID_1176097095" MODIFIED="1566553719090" TEXT="NP Completeness for dummies: Complexity Classes P and NP (lec 1)  P and NP Class Problem and Polynomial Time Solvable  The P vs NP Problem " />
