<node CREATED="1566553719090" ID="ID_772321983" MODIFIED="1566553719090" TEXT="Kruskal&#226;&#8364;&#8482;s Algorithm- Like Prim&#226;&#8364;&#8482;s Algorithm Kruskal&#226;&#8364;&#8482;s Algorithm is another greedy algorithm used for finding the Minimum Spanning Tree (MST) of a given graph.; The graph must be weighted connected and undirected. Steps for implementing Kruskal&#226;&#8364;&#8482;s Algorithm- Step-01: Sort all the edges from low weight to high weight." />
