<node CREATED="1566553719090" ID="ID_157141056" MODIFIED="1566553719090" TEXT="It is an algorithm for finding the minimum cost spanning tree of the given graph. In kruskal&#226;&#8364;&#8482;s algorithm edges are added to the spanning tree in increasing order of cost. If the edge E forms a cycle in the spanning it is discarded." />
