<node CREATED="1566553719093" ID="ID_206468376" MODIFIED="1566553719093" TEXT="In computer science 2-satisfiability 2-SAT or just 2SAT is a computational problem of assigning values to variables each of which has two possible values in order to satisfy a system of constraints on pairs of variables. It is a special case of the general Boolean satisfiability problem which can involve constraints on more than two variables and of constraint satisfaction problems " />
