<node CREATED="1566553719093" ID="ID_1635270874" MODIFIED="1566553719093" TEXT="Constraint satisfaction problems (CSPs) are mathematical questions defined as a set of objects whose state must satisfy a number of constraints or limitations. CSPs represent the entities in a problem as a homogeneous collection of finite constraints over variables which is solved by constraint satisfaction methods." />
